main event: Multiple witnesses observed a strange, luminous object in the sky over Naknek, Alaska, on January 8, 1961.
interesting points: The object was approximately 6-10 feet in diameter with bright lights that pulsated and blinked in sequence., The observation lasted for about 45 seconds., The object was reported to be traveling in a straight line towards the east., Witnesses mentioned having seen similar objects with high speed and maneuverability in the past five years., The weather condition was dark and clear during the sighting.
sighted object: strange, luminous object with bright lights
witness description: fishers from Naknek, Alaska, aged 28 and 37
